reviewText: My husband loves this movie and the tin that it came in is great.
POOR VIDEO QUALITY ON BOTH DVDS. I would not purchase any of TMG videos again.
The "Sitting Bull" DVD was purchased to replace a VHS copy that I already had, and the "Cry Blood Apache" was a bonus ! ! !

Sitting Bull / Cry Blood Apache - 2 DVD Collector's Edition Embossed Tin
This is not a review of the cast of characters, storylines or any of the like;  BE AWARE THAT THE TWO CDS JUST DO NOT PLAY....YOU CAN'T PLAY THEM YOU CAN'T RATE THEM.

(One star is being quite generous!!)

EIH
